{"data":[{"date":"09:15 19/07","title":"Perotti: \"Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Alisson v\u00e0o tay Liverpool\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Perotti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Alisson.</h2><h2>Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-liverpool-sap-co-alisson-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191535.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng sau khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Roma. Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Giallorossi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 l\u1ea7n sau 37 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho Roma t\u1ea1i Serie A. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Juventus. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.</div>\r\n<h2>Perotti tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Roma\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perotti Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Perotti Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Perotti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, Roma \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Nainggolan v\u00e0o tay Inter. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Salah c\u0169ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng Perotti cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 </span>l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ef1 h\u1ee7y ho\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh c\u1ea3. M\u1ed7i b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng xem Roma \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng lu\u00f4n thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Salah v\u00e0 Nainggolan. Nh\u01b0ng Roma s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, Roma \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00e1 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n khi \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1edbi 7 t\u00e2n binh: Javier Pastore, Justin Kluivert, Ante Coric, Davide Santon, Nicolo Zaniolo, William Bianda v\u00e0 Antonio Mirante.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Roma:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4377","checkdouble":"191568"},{"date":"11:01 19/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng: \u0110\u00e0n em Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Drogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/doi-thu-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-dan-em-luis-suarez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Qatar \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Qatar. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qatar t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Doha t\u1eeb 16-23/9 nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ecd x\u00e1t cho U19 Qatar tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0110\u00e0n em Luis Suarez  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0110\u00e0n em Luis Suarez  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/doi-thu-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-dan-em-luis-suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qatar c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Qatar s\u1ebd tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0103n t\u1eadp \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 U19 Uruguay v\u00e0 U19 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0. T\u1ea1i VCK U20 World Cup 2017, U20 Uruguay khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 chung cu\u1ed9c.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c nhau l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1eebng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n cho r\u1eb1ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e1m m\u01a1 th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau: \"\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb. D\u00f9 kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 18/10 - 4/11 t\u1ea1i Indonesia. \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u00e0 U19 Australia, U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 U19 Jordan.\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dna-168-190845.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (KT): Chia tay gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 trong n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-gio-thi-dau-u19-viet-nam-con-co-hoi-vuot-qua-vong-bang-u19-dna-168-190749.html\">\u0110\u1ed5i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng U19 \u0110N\u00c1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-168-190686.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay-372-190607.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-1 U19 Indonesia (KT): T\u00ednh to\u00e1n sai l\u1ea7m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-thoai-mai-tam-ly-truoc-tran-cau-sinh-tu-voi-u19-indonesia-168-190579.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4376","checkdouble":"191582"},{"date":"10:13 19/07","title":"Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 l\u1ea5y Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/21/barca-doi-dembele-lay-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u00e1n Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hazard \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge</span> h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u00fap m\u1edf r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Ph\u00e1p cho th\u1ea5y Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dembele Hazard\" title=\"Dembele Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/100030-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Dembele l\u1ea5y Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Barcelona c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1eafm \u0111\u1eb1ng chu\u00f4i v\u1ee5 Hazard. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Blues v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1eed th\u00e1ch s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Chelsea b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a sao tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Dembele m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 96.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 135.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sao tr\u1ebb 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Camp Nou. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb g\u1eafn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chia tay Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Chelsea v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n Hazard r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois.<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4375","checkdouble":"191575"},{"date":"09:42 19/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng Real r\u00f3t v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/real-chi-400-trieu-euro-vao-chuyen-nhuong-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez h\u1ee9a \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Liverpool \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid. R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt sau khi ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ghi trung b\u00ecnh 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/ m\u00f9a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. V\u00e0 Real bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/real-chi-400-trieu-euro-vao-chuyen-nhuong-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Perez h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e2n l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro Alvaro Odriozola, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 4 ng\u00f4i sao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Zinedine Zidane t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, Real nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Julen Lopetegui tr\u00e1m ch\u1ed7 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. V\u00e0 sau cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u00f9ng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Perez c\u00f9ng c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0a ra: Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y cho 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard\" title=\"Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 Hazard n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Eden Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real nh\u1eafm Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe song v\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i gia PSG. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, n\u01a1i Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady l\u00e0 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 Raphael Varane. Los Blancos t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Leonardo Bonucci, m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi song kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Real s\u1ebd g\u00f5 c\u1eeda Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i Ronaldo. HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebf th\u1eeba cho Luka Modric s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chu-tich-la-liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-187-191544.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo chia tay Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/theo-hernandez-sap-roi-real-180-191512.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4374","checkdouble":"191579"},{"date":"09:12 19/07","title":"Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng \u201cd\u1eb1n m\u1eb7t\u201d Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luke Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh M.U. Anh hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho trong \u0111\u1ee3t du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Shaw v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2015/16, ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o Luke Shaw t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. Sau khi HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00ean thay Louis van Gaal v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean bi \u0111\u00e1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Shaw ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1edbi 17 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Southampton c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/Shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho Mourinho th\u1eddi gian qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Shaw m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0o tay l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Ashley Young. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb HLV Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, Luke Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh M.U. &ldquo;5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i th\u1eed s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu&rdquo;, Shaw n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Luke Shaw\" title=\"hau ve Luke Shaw\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n cho Mourinho th\u1ea5y trong 4 tu\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn&rdquo;, Shaw n\u00f3i th\u00eam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV kh\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi s\u1ebd t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"Bong da\" type=\"Bong da\">Bongda24h.vn</span>:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rooney-phat-bieu-ve-mu-va-cuoc-dua-vo-dich-172-191513.html\">Rooney tin M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Man City m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-su-ra-di-cua-daley-blind-172-191510.html\">Mourinho c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Daley Blind?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/me-ronaldo-khong-the-tro-lai-mu-la-dieu-dang-tiec-172-191474.html\">M\u1eb9 Ronaldo: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia-172-191421.html\">M.U chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4373","checkdouble":"191573"},{"date":"10:30 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch ti\u00eau ti\u1ec1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u201cbu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ti\u00eau ti\u1ec1n\u201d, nh\u01b0ng t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd - HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, t\u00e2n HLV Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Sarri \u01b0u ti\u00ean &ldquo;d\u1eb9p lo\u1ea1n&rdquo; ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c s\u1eb5n c\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia Italia cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung chung. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt HLV ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i &ndash; nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB. V\u1ec1 Jorginho, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng, Chelsea \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap CLB thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao. V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u thay \u0111\u1ed5i 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng xem \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t &ndash; Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Eden Hazard, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c ai ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh &ndash; trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u0169 trang. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Chelsea \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Golovin &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chelsea-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-pho-ta-sarri-172-191564.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri</span><br>\r\nGianfranco Zola \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1nh tay ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Chelsea m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong-172-191562.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong-172-191562.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4372","checkdouble":"191577"},{"date":"11:31 19/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Liverpool chi ti\u1ec1n thay th\u1ebf Karius","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/huyen-thoai-ung-ho-liverpool-chi-tien-thay-the-karius.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i The Kop, Graeme Souness \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng, Liverpool c\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf Karius ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nThe Kop ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma &ndash; v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Loris Karius trong khung g\u1ed7. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Graeme Souness chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;HLV Klopp \u0111ang \u1edf trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 trao ni\u1ec1m tin cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu Karius thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu ta ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Klopp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool c\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf Karius ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" title=\"Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/huyen-thoai-ung-ho-liverpool-chi-tien-thay-the-karius.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool c\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf Karius ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Karius ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i, v\u00e0 Liverpool c\u1ea7n \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea1m 2 l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Karius tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Karius m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan c\u1ee7a Liverpool, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd \u0111em v\u1ec1 1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i mang v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u&rdquo; &ndash; Graeme Souness \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Liverpool c\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf Karius ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi &ldquo;bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t&rdquo; t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\nLiverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp theo \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu-172-191567.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu-172-191567.html\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Alisson, Klopp \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 Liverpool v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i</span><br>\r\nKlopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1eafp c\u00f3 nh\u01b0 Alisson, \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Liverpool chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4371","checkdouble":"191586"},{"date":"11:47 19/07","title":"Mourinho b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mourinho-bao-tin-cuc-buon-ve-alexis-sanchez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn, m\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 - ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng sang M\u1ef9 tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSanchez m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t \u1edf Manchester<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn Alexis Sanchez c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb, nh\u1eb1m l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn visa \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Barca. V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, anh nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c \u00e1n 16 th\u00e1ng t\u00f9 treo, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa. V\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Los Angeles, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp chay \u1edf trung t\u00e2m Carrington trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, khi\u1ebfn Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ed1t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng sang M\u1ef9 v\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i visa\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/mourinho-bao-tin-cuc-buon-ve-alexis-sanchez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng sang M\u1ef9 v\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i visa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nN\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft CLB \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n M\u1ef9 trong v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft visa. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng Alexis Sanchez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Anthony Martial, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Man United trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng sang M\u1ef9, Mourinho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb: &ldquo;C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e0n anh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Anh \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 Premier League. BTC \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng khi b\u1eaft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-chua-gi-da-mat-tan-binh-vi-chan-thuong-172-191570.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/man-utd-chua-gi-da-mat-tan-binh-vi-chan-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-chua-gi-da-mat-tan-binh-vi-chan-thuong-172-191570.html\">Man Utd ch\u01b0a g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u00e2n binh v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong v\u00f2ng hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu-172-191573.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaw-quyet-tam-quay-tro-lai-doi-hinh-chinh-mu-172-191573.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng &ldquo;d\u1eb1n m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nLuke Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh M.U. Anh hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho trong \u0111\u1ee3t du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4370","checkdouble":"191587"},{"date":"11:10 19/07","title":"Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi \u201cbi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t\u201d t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp theo \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u\u2026</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ng\u00e3 gi\u00e1 gi\u1eefa Liverpool v\u00e0 AS Roma di\u1ec5n ra trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u201cch\u00e2n ch\u1ea5t\u201d nh\u01b0 Liverpool, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n. The Kop c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 sau khi c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 thi nh\u1ea5t, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ed1t Alisson Becker, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span>. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f3 n\u1ed5 hay kh\u00f4ng. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 66.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (75 tri\u1ec7u Euro) g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n (Ederson t\u1edbi Man City gi\u00e1 35.6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00e8 2017) v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Roma g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson Khi bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson Khi bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Liverpool-sap-co-Alisson-Khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlisson ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c t\u1edbi Liverpool. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League. T\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong m\u1eaft nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i (2015/16 v\u00e0 2016/17).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2013, Liverpool c\u1ee7a Brendan Rodgers mua Simon Mignolet v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Sunderland v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1eafc Ireland ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hay nh\u1ea5t Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u00ec sao?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMignolet ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01a1i hay \u1edf m\u00f9a 2013/14, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Liverpool th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eeb sau s\u1ef1 h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i c\u1ee7a The Kop v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng tr\u1eadn hay, tr\u1eadn d\u1edf c\u1ee7a anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson Khi bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson Khi bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/Liverpool-va-thuong-vu-Alisson-Khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mignolet...</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi Klopp sau khi l\u00ean thay Rodgers bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Loris Karius t\u1eeb Mainz v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 4.75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn ngay \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y m\u00e0 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Mainz \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Klopp c\u00f3 anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t r\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. C\u00e1i gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Mignolet hay 4.75 tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Karius n\u00f3i l\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Klopp r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, song \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Bundesliga. Dortmund c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9m Bayern Munich, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson Khi bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson Khi bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Liverpool-va-thuong-vu-Alisson-Khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">... r\u1ed3i Karius \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong tay Klopp lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i \u201cti\u1ebfng th\u01a1m\u201d cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y. Nh\u01b0ng Premier League th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. M\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4i, Liverpool c\u1ee7a HLV 51 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 thua ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u1edf 4 trong 6 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng (Stoke, Swansea v\u00e0 West Brom). \u0110\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Mignolet hay Karius c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u00edch cho The Kop ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i t\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span><br>\r\n<span>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i thay Karius. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1edbi C\u0110V Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, 2 sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Karius \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u00f4m h\u1eadn. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau khi sao s\u00e1ng Mo Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Alisson, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 mua v\u1ec1 Virgil van Dijk (75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Naby Keita (53.46 tri\u1ec7u), Fabinho (40 tri\u1ec7u) \u0111\u1ec1u trong n\u0103m 2018. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Klopp \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mignolet hay Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 ra c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ragnar Klavan, Alberto Moreno hay Joel Matip. Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 Marko Grujic, Allan, Pedro Chirivella hay Ovie Ejaria. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ho\u1eb7c thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng cao v\u00e0 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp that bai\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp that bai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/HLV-Jurgen-Klopp-that-bai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \"c\u1ee7a r\u1ebb\"</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nD\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea9y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Klopp r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Liverpool th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Dortmund. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Premier League kh\u00f4ng cho \u00f4ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, t\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u1ee7a Klopp c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. H\u00e8 2016, Liverpool chi 71.2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 6 t\u00e2n binh. H\u00e8 2017, h\u1ecd chi 82.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Mo Salah. C\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 ti\u00eang 7 th\u00e1ng r\u01b0\u1ee1i qua, t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 t\u1edbi nay, The Kop chi t\u1edbi 176.4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Naby Keita va Fabinho\" title=\"Naby Keita va Fabinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Naby-Keita-va-Fabinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXu h\u01b0\u1edbng Van Dijk \u0111ang lan t\u1ecfa t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Khi trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp, Klopp t\u1eebng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng th\u1eddi th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed9c \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ng\u00e0y Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool, tin ch\u1eafc Klopp c\u0169ng l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb g\u1ea5p g\u1ea7n 5 l\u1ea7n Mignolet v\u00e0 Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu-172-191567.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Alisson, Klopp \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 Liverpool v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i</span>. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i hay ch\u00ed \u00edt l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn thay \u0111\u1ed5i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Liverpool c\u1ee7a Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1eafng tay d\u00f9 3 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool cua Klopp mua Alisson\" title=\"Liverpool cua Klopp mua Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Klopp v\u00e0 Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKlopp kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 4. D\u00f9 Liverpool c\u00f3 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng h\u1eb3n c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh tay v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d Van Dijk \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool c\u00e0ng th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh tay tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. D\u00f9 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o, n\u1ebfu Liverpool gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, Klopp v\u1eabn \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee9c th\u1eddi, b\u1ecf \u0111i c\u00e1i c\u0169 d\u00f9 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tru-cot-172-191551.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/perotti-roma-se-song-tot-khi-alisson-ra-di-176-191568.html\">Perotti: Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Alisson v\u00e0o tay Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool-172-191445.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-nguoi-bi-quen-lang-172-191409.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/grujic-roi-liverpool-sang-cardiff-172-191368.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4369","checkdouble":"191590"},{"date":"07:37 19/07","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Florentino Perez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng Cristiano Ronaldo.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Hazard thay Ronaldo?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang \u1edf Bernabeu nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-he-2018-hua-hen-se-no-bom-tan-sau-CR7-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau khi chia tay si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eafm vai ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 g\u1ea7n th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 \u0111\u00e3 qua, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh Los Blancos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c b\u1ea1o chi h\u01a1n sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c bom t\u1ea5n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, cam \u0111oan c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Real Madrid trong m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d \u2013 Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft Alvaro Odriozola, t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro mua t\u1eeb Valencia v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3, lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ti\u1ebfp theo.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady nh\u1ea5t cho hay, Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea</span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u201c\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3\u201d s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Julen Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4368","checkdouble":"191561"},{"date":"08:49 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/tan-binh-odriozola-tri-an-hlv-lopetegui-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alvaro Odriozola h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui. Anh c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Odriozola h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Lopetegui</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"http://bongdaplus.vn/alvaro-odriozola-tan-binh-cua-real-madrid-la-ai-2218061807.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u00e2n binh Odriozola</span> m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real h\u00f4m qua sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Real v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u00e0 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Sociedad n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 35 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu, Odriozola c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Lopetegui. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Odriozola v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 thay v\u00ec hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Sergi Roberto v\u00e0 Hector Bellerin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/tan-binh-odriozola-tri-an-hlv-lopetegui-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV\u00a0Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m Odriozola c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 HLV Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 trao cho t\u00f4i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u1ea1i Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u00e1ng nay. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u cao. V\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Lopetegui th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Real b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Lopetegui kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c khi Zidane r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo c\u0169ng ra \u0111i. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real thay m\u00e1u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRonaldo l\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo-180-191561.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4367","checkdouble":"191566"},{"date":"07:13 19/07","title":"Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/jose-mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-chieu-mo-tan-binh-vo-danh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba sau qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Fred v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot, ngay sau khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chia-tay-johnstone-172-190315.html\" target=\"_blank\">chia tay \u201cc\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn\u201d Sam Johnstones</span> c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/jose-mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-chieu-mo-tan-binh-vo-danh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 35 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n th\u1ee9 ba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero trong khung g\u1ed7 Old Trafford. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong khung g\u1ed7 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Joel Perreira.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jose Mourinho l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh ra m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 22 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mua Lee Grant b\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Joel Perreira ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i ch\u01a1i x\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn hai n\u0103m tr\u1eddi \u1edf c\u00e1i tu\u1ed5i 22 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 Lee, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea3 Championship c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Joel ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng Joel \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em \u0111i m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh ai-c\u0169ng-kh\u00f4ng-bi\u1ebft-l\u00e0-ai</span><br>\r\nManchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4366","checkdouble":"191560"},{"date":"08:40 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea: \u201cN\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois v\u1ec1 tay Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 vinh danh nh\u1eefng Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c Eden Hazard hay G\u0103ng Tay V\u00e0ng Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng ni\u1ec1m vui kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Chelsea khi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 tay Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Hazard tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</span>, Courtois c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng r\u1eb1ng\u2026 Hazard \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u, anh theo \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy\u1ec7t chi \u0111\u1ebfn 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c th\u00e0nh London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Hazard ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho Maurizio Sarri khi c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u1ea5m ch\u1ed7 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00e2n HLV 59 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh m\u1ea5t \u0111i hai ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ngay khi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Chelsea c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu HLV h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi n\u00f3, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec c\u00f3 trong tay, v\u1eady n\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea5m Hazard n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i h\u1ecfi han Hazard trong l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau World Cup. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 4-5 ng\u00e0y trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho Chelsea.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Eden Hazard n\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 an t\u1ecda \u1edf m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4365","checkdouble":"191562"}]}